She glared at them. "Assassins don't scare me. Killing takes little skill 
now a days.  It's not getting killed that requires greater skill." She saw 
him take a step back.  She lowered her dagger and kept it by her side.  But 
she held on to it just in case.  Until Megatron said so, she would not trust 
them.
